---
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Sidebar from "../../components/Sidebar.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html>
  <Header title="Homelab | Matheus Boscariol" seoTitle="Homelab | Matheus Boscariol" description="My homelab is a growing creation of mine. Started in 2021, it has gained many services and gone through major overhauls." pageUrl="https://matheusbosc.com/projects/homelab" />
  <body>
    <div class="content">
      <Sidebar selectedItem="devops" />
      <nav class="main">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="back-nav-container">
            <a
              href="javascript:history.back()"
              class="back-nav-button w-inline-block"
              ><img
                src="/assets/back.svg"
                loading="lazy"
                alt=""
                class="back-nav-img"
              />
              <div>Back</div></a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="content-container">
            <h1>Homelab</h1>
            <section class="items-container">
              <div class="resouce-items">
                <div class="single-item">
                  <p>
                    <strong>Personal Cloud & Infrastructure Playground</strong>
                  </p>
                  <br />
                  <p>
                    <strong>Stack:</strong> Linux, Docker, Cloudflare, Reverse Proxies
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    <strong>Status:</strong> Active & Evolving
                  </p>

                  <blockquote>
                    A personal lab environment to experiment with networking,
                    cloud deployment, container orchestration, and
                    infrastructure automation.
                  </blockquote>
                </div>

                <div class="single-item">
                  <h3>Key Highlights</h3>
                  <ul role="list">
                    <li>
                      Hosts multiple web services, game servers, and automation
                      tools.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Fully automated with CI/CD pipelines for deployment and
                      updates.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Includes monitoring, logging, and secure external access
                      via Cloudflare.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Designed for learning, testing, and scaling infrastructure
                      safely.
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <!--<div class="single-item">
                  <h3>Visual / Diagram</h3>

                  Insert a simplified network diagram or architecture GIF here
                  
                  Public internet → Cloudflare → Reverse Proxy → Dockerized
                  services 
                  
                  Services include: web apps, game servers, dev tools,
                  media servers
                  
                </div> -->

                <div class="single-item">
                  <a href="/assets/projects/homelab/pve.png"
                    ><img
                      class="project-display"
                      src="/assets/projects/homelab/pve.png"
                      style="max-width: 49.5%;"
                    /></a
                  >
                  <a href="/assets/projects/homelab/portainer.png"
                    ><img
                      class="project-display"
                      src="/assets/projects/homelab/portainer.png"
                      style="max-width: 49.5%;"
                    /></a
                  >
                </div>

                <div class="single-item">
                  <h3>Challenges & Solutions</h3>
                  <ul role="list">
                    <li>
                      <strong>Network Segmentation:</strong> Isolated services using VLANs and Docker networks to prevent interference.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <strong>Secure Remote Access:</strong> Implemented zero-trust access and Cloudflare tunnels.
                    </li>
                    <!--
                    <li>
                      <strong>Automation:</strong> CI/CD pipelines automatically deploy container updates with minimal downtime.
                    </li>
                    -->
                    <li>
                      <strong>Resource Optimization:</strong> Used virtualization and Docker to maximize hardware efficiency.
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="single-item">
                  <a href="/assets/projects/homelab/jellyfin.png"
                    ><img
                      class="project-display"
                      src="/assets/projects/homelab/jellyfin.png"
                      style="max-width: 49.5%;"
                    /></a
                  >
                  <a href="/assets/projects/homelab/jellyseer.png"
                    ><img
                      class="project-display"
                      src="/assets/projects/homelab/jellyseer.png"
                      style="max-width: 49.5%;"
                    /></a
                  >
                </div>

                <div class="single-item">
                  <h3>Lessons Learned</h3>
                  <ul role="list">
                    <li>
                      Gained practical experience in <strong>network security</strong> and <strong>service orchestration</strong>.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Learned the trade-offs between <strong>simplicity vs. flexibility</strong> in homelab setups.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Practiced <strong>monitoring, logging, and troubleshooting</strong> in a controlled environment.
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="single-item">
                  <a href="/assets/projects/homelab/ha.png"
                    ><img
                      class="project-display"
                      src="/assets/projects/homelab/ha.png"
                      style="max-width: 49.5%;"
                    /></a
                  >
                  <a href="/assets/projects/homelab/vault.png"
                    ><img
                      class="project-display"
                      src="/assets/projects/homelab/vault.png"
                      style="max-width: 49.5%;"
                    /></a
                  >
                </div>

              
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <!--[if lte IE 9]><script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/placeholders/3.0.2/placeholders.min.js"></script><![endif]-->
  </body>
</html>
